body:
This allows linking together with runCommands as expected.

Part of #10121

This works now:

```json
{
  "key": "ctrl+alt+`",
  "command": "runCommands",
  "args": {
    "commands": [
      "workbench.action.createTerminalEditor",
      "workbench.action.experimentalMoveEditorIntoNewWindowAction"
    ]
  }
}
```
